 },
 {
  "text": "Hi Graziele, this is Dr. Carter. Thank you again for the welcome yesterday. I have a question about your role. You work with many doctors and many departments, so you are the right person. Who is the coordinator for the cardiology team? Please send me the name and the role. I want to talk to your colleague about a new project. Thank you, and talk soon.",
